{"tid":731414,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底女人係咩黎","createTime":"2018-07-06T07:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T08:06:26.000Z","uid":92201,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc081ef10e4e3ad23e0999b83823fc48289c4da8","tid":731414,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"感覺佢地好似外星人咁<br />\n<br />\n同男人講野都仲可以正常啲講自己想講既野, 但係女人真係唔知點講好, <br />\n<br />\n平時好似無野, 但係自動會比人討厭, 真心唔知自己錯咩.<br />\n<br />\n結果大過之後自自然然會覺得女人似異形, 公司平時同同事都吹到, 間唔中有個女人過黎返工真係好撚慘, 成個office本身得兩個位, 我長坐一個, 搵個女既黎返工, office靜到得返打字聲, 唉<br />\n<br />\n到底女人係咩黎"},{"pid":"b2ab0e1f378072581b70437819587a720ab6d415","tid":731414,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"17b46ee9ef633f6271db525fa8e82e29387420e4","tid":731414,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2ab0e1f378072581b70437819587a720ab6d415","tid":731414,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"連登標準答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}